quote.summary: Huitongda Network Co Ltd, formerly formerly Jiangsu Huitongda Supply Chain Management Co Ltd, is a China-based company mainly engaged in supply chain retail business. The Company's main business is sales of a comprehensive suite of merchandise in lower tier cities and rural areas and provision of intelligent business and marketing subscription service, offering merchant solutions and rendering other various related services. The Company conducts its operations through two segments. The Commerce Business segment mainly includes direct sales and provision of marketplace service that enables merchants to sell their products to transacting users through the online platform. The Service Business segment, which mainly represents the provision of intelligent business and marketing software as a service (SaaS+) subscription service and a collection of merchant solutions. The Company mainly conducts its businesses in the domestic market.
